cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the detection of adversarial examples in the visual perception of autonomous vehicles. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the vulnerability of neural networks to adversarial examples and proposes a detection algorithm. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the impact of adversarial examples on autonomous systems. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is a relevant category as the paper focuses on autonomous driving and the impact of adversarial examples on the perception pipeline. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the security of autonomous systems against adversarial attacks.
